                  <provenance notBefore="1500" notAfter="1525">‘<persName key="person_4602"
                        role="sgn">Iohn morysson</persName> williham denys gentylman of myddylsex’
                     (fol. 65, upper margin; s. xvi in.).</provenance>
                  <provenance when="1562">‘liber <persName key="person_2770" role="fmo">Henrici
                        dotyn</persName> 1562’ (fol. iiiv). He was a Fellow of Exeter 1554–60 and in
                     1558 owned <ref
                        target="https://medieval.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/catalog/manuscript_479">BodL, MS
                        Auct. D.4.9</ref>.</provenance>
